divs: Sighting DetailsWhen I first saw it, it was right over my head. I was in a restaurant sitting out doors next to the water. I was eating alone so when looked up and saw this strange object and strange light patterns moving so quiet and yet so close I was shocked. I did take out my phone and was able to get video evidence but by the time I started recording the UFO was already on the other side of the bay. I was still able to capture on video the UFO actually disappearing right in front of your eyes and re appear again. It also descended as if to land. I have this evidence on my phone and will be more than happy to show you.
